title: Grateful Dead Live at Providence Civic Center on 1986-03-30
lineage: Cassette Master (Nakamichi CR-7A) > Tascam DA-3000 (DSF 1-bit/5.8 MHz) > KORG AudioGate 4 > FLAC; Edited & Mastered in Audacity by Joe Noel: Flac 24/96; Checksum & tags created in xACT
description:
Set 1

Hell In A Bucket-> Sugaree, El Paso-> Cumberland Blues, Tons Of Steel, CC Rider, Dupree's Diamond Blues, Just Like Tom Thumb's Blues-> Deal

Set 2

Touch Of Gray-> Samson & Delilah, Terrapin Station-> Women Are Smarter-> Drums-> Why Don't We Do It In The Road-> Stella Blue-> Throwing Stones-> Not Fade Away, E:Not Fade Away-> E: The Mighty Quinn
